ActRadiocommunication Act
PrecisEnactment of the RADIOCOMMUNICATION ACT (SUBSECTION 4(1) AND PARAGRAPH 9(1)(B)) EXEMPTION ORDER (SECURITY, SAFETY AND INTERNATIONAL RELATIONS), NO. 2009-1 - which exempts the RCMP from the application of this Act with respect to interfering with radiocommunication signals during the visit to Canada in February 2009 of United States President Barack Obama.
